{"tid":1048323,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家遇過最無公德心嘅大陸人行為","createTime":"2019-03-05T14:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T15:41:57.000Z","uid":216185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffdc178702dae49f0f038527ec735726e9cb6eea","tid":1048323,"uid":216185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母頭先搭火車有個大陸閪喺撚咁R個頭 <br />\n<br />\n我本來都唔覺有咩事<br />\n<br />\n然後我眼角「哨」到條撚樣 心諗樣做乜鳩R咁撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(R撚咗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要間唔時又R下)<br />\n<br />\n之後我抬起頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見條撚屌360度 全方位喺度R個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">頭皮</span>喺佢隔離不停地散落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nR完仲要又撥落地又吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重要飛埋嚟我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母大陸人真喺唔撚死都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/222751_57d133bb22353bcb0beb53ea39c3226c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F222751_57d133bb22353bcb0beb53ea39c3226c.png&h=29b33c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/222752_173454cc33226007cbb13961ad8035e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F222752_173454cc33226007cbb13961ad8035e4.png&h=1649545b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/222754_cb882b1391419ae93984a2772eaa777a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F222754_cb882b1391419ae93984a2772eaa777a.png&h=b34f7a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/222755_372561103f941eee2395c2d3a89f6ccc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F222755_372561103f941eee2395c2d3a89f6ccc.png&h=6185c031&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/222757_2560c6c891272533ae21941a5ac59f19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F222757_2560c6c891272533ae21941a5ac59f19.png&h=07b299e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae5ee691ae41b950b659b329c1fe94bb53b38e20","tid":1048323,"uid":216185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f74b67852a1ad2396361af82b3423b7a0cfd8c1","tid":1048323,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"去垃圾房扔垃圾<br />\n個垃圾桶都無三分一滿<br />\n佢竟然就噉放低喺垃圾桶格離<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/230839_67e5bf1802ee1d6e5db6e25a4e7e1751.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F230839_67e5bf1802ee1d6e5db6e25a4e7e1751.png&h=6bae5252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"579752f07dcc637bcb2781204e225167c2b3cf4e","tid":1048323,"uid":159568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"隨地吐痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 核突到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6a87550d611fcd9b8f182da3